ANGULAR CMD:

sudo npm install @angular/cli@latest : installs the latest version of angular
ng new {projectName} : creates the new project will all the required modules
ng serve : Will start the server on localhost:4200

npm install --save bootstrap@4:  Install the CSS bootstrap in node_moules
	node_modules/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css : include this in angular.json of section architect section of styles
ng g c {componentName} : Creates the all the required template for components and also do the necessary imports and DI



npm install --save-dev @angular/cli@latest : Your global Angular CLI version  is greater than your local

json-server --watch src/assets/forms/tabarrayform.json : Json Server watch

